Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.76,0:00:11.72,Main,,0,0,0,,There exists a room of sorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.72,0:00:16.39,Main,,0,0,0,,The view from the window can be seen clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.39,0:00:19.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Everyone besides me looks happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.06,0:00:26.98,Main,,0,0,0,,It feels like I'm the only one who hasn't\Nmoved in this ever-changing world.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.98,0:00:32.74,Main,,0,0,0,,In this separated room, I waited\Nfor the day I could go outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.74,0:00:34.83,Main,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.83,0:00:37.79,Main,,0,0,0,,...that room has no doors.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.79,0:00:39.79,Main,,0,0,0,,So, I wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.79,0:00:45.96,Main,,0,0,0,,...for the world outside the window\Nto stop, just like how it is in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.96,0:00:48.05,Main,,0,0,0,,My only...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.05,0:00:49.38,Main,,0,0,0,,...wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.73,0:01:09.23,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Taken and granted,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.23,0:01:13.24,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ideals are repetitious games that slip through{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.24,0:01:15.95,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My daily life is so shot with holes{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.95,0:01:18.83,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}that I can barely stand{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.83,0:01:20.12,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Empty theories without conclusions{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.12,0:01:24.33,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dance steps along invisible rules{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.33,0:01:29.34,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The final bell holding together{\i0}\N{\i1}the crumbling day rings{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.34,0:01:33.76,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In the scene I imagine{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.76,0:01:36.39,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}you're there{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.39,0:01:39.22,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}with a smile{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.22,0:01:44.73,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No forgiveness? No desires?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.73,0:01:48.15,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And still{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.82,0:01:52.99,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We cry "OPEN"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.99,0:01:57.28,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A future to get back and a world to destroy{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.28,0:01:59.74,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A wish to open. GOT IT?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.74,0:02:01.41,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now cross{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.41,0:02:04.08,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wish you don't cry{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.08,0:02:11.09,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The future of light and dark,{\i0}\N{\i1}let's believe in the "future"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.09,0:02:17.59,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}so that they overlap to gain color again{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.81,0:02:22.14,Main,,0,0,0,,You surprised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.14,0:02:24.64,Main,,0,0,0,,I didn't think you would come.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.64,0:02:27.35,Main,,0,0,0,,You're the one who tipped us off.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.35,0:02:29.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.11,0:02:31.36,Main,,0,0,0,,I did want to talk with you about something.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.36,0:02:32.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.82,0:02:37.82,Main,,0,0,0,,You hate me... right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.32,0:02:40.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.45,0:02:42.75,Main,,0,0,0,,How far did you go...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.75,0:02:45.71,Main,,0,0,0,,How far?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.71,0:02:47.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Just a kiss...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.96,0:02:48.92,Main,,0,0,0,,K-Ki...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.92,0:02:51.17,Main,,0,0,0,,I-It can't be helped!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.17,0:02:54.47,Main,,0,0,0,,That was my wish, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.47,0:02:58.93,Main,,0,0,0,,All Hanayo-{\i1}san {\i0}did was\Nmake my wish come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.93,0:03:03.35,Main,,0,0,0,,I-I mean I did want to, um...\Nkiss him sooner than later!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.35,0:03:04.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Kiss...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.60,0:03:10.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Wha...?! Wh-What is it, Hanayo-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.06,0:03:13.19,Main,,0,0,0,,You haven't changed at all\Neven after being an LRIG.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.19,0:03:14.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Straightforward and gullible...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.94,0:03:16.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.28,0:03:19.78,Main,,0,0,0,,...easily hurt, yet desperately\Ntrying to look strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.78,0:03:22.08,Main,,0,0,0,,You really...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.08,0:03:24.29,Main,,0,0,0,,...are similar to Kazuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.58,0:03:30.25,Main,,0,0,0,,I approached Kazuki to fulfill your wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.25,0:03:32.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Kazuki is just like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.46,0:03:37.09,Main,,0,0,0,,--Isn't that...?\N--Eew...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.09,0:03:38.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Gross...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.14,0:03:48.48,Main,,0,0,0,,At first, all I wanted to do\Nwas to fulfill your wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.48,0:03:50.56,Main,,0,0,0,,But, I soon realized...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.56,0:03:53.19,Main,,0,0,0,,...that I was in love with Kazuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.19,0:03:54.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Hanayo-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.11,0:03:57.40,Main,,0,0,0,,That's why... I can't do this anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.40,0:04:01.82,Main,,0,0,0,,I love Kazuki, but I also like you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.82,0:04:06.04,Main,,0,0,0,,If finding happiness with\NKazuki becomes my wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.04,0:04:08.58,Main,,0,0,0,,...that would be a betrayal to you, Yuzuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.58,0:04:09.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Hanayo-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.54,0:04:11.42,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't want that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.42,0:04:14.34,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't betray you... deceive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.34,0:04:17.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Kazuki thinks that I'm you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.30,0:04:19.63,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't continue doing this to my precious--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.39,0:04:25.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Kazuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.76,0:04:28.35,Main,,0,0,0,,What was that about, Yuzuki...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.35,0:04:30.69,Main,,0,0,0,,What was that you were saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.31,0:04:34.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.15,0:04:35.32,Main,,0,0,0,,No...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.53,0:04:39.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.36,0:04:40.65,Main,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.65,0:04:42.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Kazuki, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.28,0:04:46.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Kazuki, you're not a Selector,\Nso you can't hear Yuzuki's voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.45,0:04:47.83,Main,,0,0,0,,H-Hanayo-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.83,0:04:51.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki's voice? Hanayo-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.12,0:04:54.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki... I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.17,0:04:58.34,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't... fulfill your wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.34,0:05:00.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait, Hanayo-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.05,0:05:02.63,Main,,0,0,0,,--Yuzuki!\N--Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.63,0:05:07.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Please listen to our story... Yuzuki's story!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.26,0:05:09.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki's story...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.32,0:05:18.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Why don't they understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.86,0:05:23.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Even the ones I created\Nare leaving me behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.95,0:05:27.54,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll be beside you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.88,0:05:35.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Hanayo-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.30,0:05:41.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Hanayo-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.97,0:05:44.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Hanayo-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.47,0:05:46.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.06,0:05:50.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Where's Hanayo-{\i1}san{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.73,0:05:55.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Hanayo-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.48,0:05:57.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Continue to fulfill my wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.48,0:06:01.15,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't care if you betray me, so live my wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.15,0:06:03.99,Main,,0,0,0,,If not, you're going to die, Hanayo-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.99,0:06:06.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Calm down, Yuzuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.79,0:06:11.62,Main,,0,0,0,,It's okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.62,0:06:14.04,Main,,0,0,0,,She'll be fine, Yuzuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.17,0:06:24.84,Main,,0,0,0,,You're going to believe us?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.84,0:06:30.31,Main,,0,0,0,,I can definitely feel Yuzuki's\Npresence from this card.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.31,0:06:34.48,Main,,0,0,0,,An Eternal Girl that doesn't\Nfulfill their wish disappears.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.48,0:06:36.60,Main,,0,0,0,,We need to save Hanayo-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.60,0:06:39.02,Main,,0,0,0,,I need to hurry and become an LRIG...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.02,0:06:42.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko, you have one win.\NIf you can win a few more, then--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.44,0:06:44.03,Main,,0,0,0,,There's not enough time!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.03,0:06:46.20,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll battle once!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.20,0:06:49.20,Main,,0,0,0,,You can battle again as long as\Nit isn't the same LRIG, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.20,0:06:51.45,Main,,0,0,0,,All we have to do is split up\Nand find Selectors--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.45,0:06:53.00,Main,,0,0,0,,It'll be too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.00,0:06:55.33,Main,,0,0,0,,In that time, Hanayo-{\i1}san {\i0}will...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.33,0:06:56.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.83,0:06:58.88,Main,,0,0,0,,...you don't have to win multiple times.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.88,0:07:00.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.59,0:07:04.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko, you're just like how\NI was when I was a Selector.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.34,0:07:08.85,Main,,0,0,0,,You were already in a state\Nto have your wish granted.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.85,0:07:11.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama didn't accept your wish, Ruko, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.56,0:07:13.35,Main,,0,0,0,,...an Eternal Girl wasn't born.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.35,0:07:14.31,Main,,0,0,0,,That means...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.31,0:07:20.94,Main,,0,0,0,,If Tama is willing to accept...\NRuko's wish can come true?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.94,0:07:26.03,Main,,0,0,0,,But, you can't go to the white window\Nroom without being an LRIG, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.03,0:07:29.03,Main,,0,0,0,,The battlefield is linked\Nto the white window room.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.03,0:07:29.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.99,0:07:33.79,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll try calling out for Tama during battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.79,0:07:36.04,Main,,0,0,0,,If my voice can reach Tama...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.04,0:07:39.33,Main,,0,0,0,,...then my wish can be granted.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.01,0:07:51.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.68,0:07:53.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Um, Hitoe?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.68,0:07:55.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Can you ask Kazuki something in place of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.98,0:07:57.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.02,0:07:59.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Whether he loves me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.69,0:08:03.86,Main,,0,0,0,,...or whether he loves Hanayo-{\i1}san {\i0}in my form...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.86,0:08:04.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.65,0:08:06.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah! N-Never mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.65,0:08:08.40,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll ask him myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.40,0:08:10.62,Main,,0,0,0,,...when I'm released from the card!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.62,0:08:11.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Right, Ruko?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.74,0:08:12.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.79,0:08:16.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Open!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.55,0:08:30.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Is... this it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.80,0:08:36.43,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't... meet Ru anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.36,0:08:52.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe! Don't try to lose on purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.78,0:08:56.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Only serious battles will make Ru shine,\Nand light the way to Tama!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.66,0:08:58.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Got it! Yuzuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.37,0:09:00.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Of course! I'm not going to go easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.91,0:09:02.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Fiery Ambition!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.42,0:09:06.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.50,0:09:07.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Who...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.55,0:09:08.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.67,0:09:10.97,Main,,0,0,0,,That voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.97,0:09:12.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.85,0:09:17.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Who is... Yuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.51,0:09:19.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.23,0:09:24.56,Main,,0,0,0,,It's me... Kuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.56,0:09:28.74,Main,,0,0,0,,But... I'm not Kuro anymore. I'm Yuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.74,0:09:32.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Just like you, Ru gave me a name...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.03,0:09:33.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.25,0:09:46.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama... We were born from Mayu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.63,0:09:47.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Yup...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.80,0:09:51.09,Main,,0,0,0,,But, the person who gave us our names...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.09,0:09:55.26,Main,,0,0,0,,The person who taught us\Nof the outside world was Ru.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.26,0:09:57.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Yup...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.10,0:10:00.10,Main,,0,0,0,,So, let's show our gratitude...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.10,0:10:02.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Together we'll grant Ru's wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.81,0:10:03.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.48,0:10:10.07,Main,,0,0,0,,We'll win this battle in the next turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.07,0:10:11.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.44,0:10:12.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.45,0:10:15.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuki...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.12,0:10:22.41,Main,,0,0,0,,I accept...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.54,0:10:27.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.51,0:10:40.81,Main,,0,0,0,,...the laws of the Selector.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.81,0:10:42.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.94,0:10:50.48,Main,,0,0,0,,...a new Eternal Girl will be born!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.95,0:10:59.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.16,0:11:06.62,Main,,0,0,0,,What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.50,0:11:10.96,Main,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.44,0:11:27.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.64,0:11:29.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Is Yuzuki back, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.65,0:11:30.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.94,0:11:32.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.23,0:11:34.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Was the wish... granted?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.03,0:11:36.28,Main,,0,0,0,,B-But, something's not right...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.28,0:11:38.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuki's card didn't change either...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.45,0:11:41.78,Main,,0,0,0,,There has to be some sort of\Nchange with the wish being granted.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.78,0:11:46.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Um... I might be wrong,\Nbut can I say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.54,0:11:50.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko-{\i1}san {\i0}did this battle so that she\Ncould go to the white window room...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.29,0:11:52.46,Main,,0,0,0,,...to meet this girl, Mayu, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.46,0:11:54.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.55,0:11:57.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Is that the only place she's at?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.05,0:11:58.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.30,0:12:04.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Mayu created a world of Selector battles so that\Nshe can escape from her harsh realities, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.68,0:12:09.98,Main,,0,0,0,,If so, maybe she's suffering\Neven now, in this real world, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.98,0:12:11.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Th-That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.56,0:12:16.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Even if we don't go to the white window room,\Nif we can convince the real Mayu, then...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.61,0:12:20.87,Main,,0,0,0,,But if that's the case,\Nwhy didn't Yuki tell us that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.95,0:12:23.99,Main,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Hitoe?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.99,0:12:29.00,Main,,0,0,0,,That place we had a glimpse of\Nbefore exiting the battlefield...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.00,0:12:31.46,Main,,0,0,0,,The white window room!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.46,0:12:37.26,Main,,0,0,0,,If that's it, then I recall\Nseeing a place like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.27,0:12:50.52,Main,,0,0,0,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.52,0:12:52.15,Main,,0,0,0,,...Mayu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.15,0:12:54.65,Main,,0,0,0,,You're so stupid...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.65,0:12:58.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Shiro is playing hide-and-seek now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.40,0:13:02.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Even if Kuro and Shiro's feelings are in sync...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.74,0:13:06.16,Main,,0,0,0,,...without Shiro, your wish won't come true...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.16,0:13:09.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Mayu, please listen to what we have to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.41,0:13:11.62,Main,,0,0,0,,What did you just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.62,0:13:13.46,Main,,0,0,0,,P-Please listen to--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.46,0:13:17.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Kuro... Did you just say "we"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.38,0:13:19.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Kuro, you're supposed to be all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.63,0:13:23.30,Main,,0,0,0,,The word "we" isn't a word that fits Kuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.18,0:13:29.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Her name isn't "Kuro!" It's "Yuki!"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.81,0:13:31.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.94,0:13:33.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Lame...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.56,0:13:38.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Like, seasons don't mean anything\Nwhen you're trapped inside a card!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.65,0:13:40.11,Main,,0,0,0,,What an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.11,0:13:42.03,Main,,0,0,0,,She's just an LRIG!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.03,0:13:45.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuki's feelings are Mayu's feelings...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.16,0:13:48.33,Main,,0,0,0,,...and Tama's too...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.33,0:13:50.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Both of them were born from Mayu...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.83,0:13:55.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Together, they form your true feelings...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.17,0:14:03.63,Main,,0,0,0,,You sought protection with snow that won't\Nharm you, covering everything in silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.63,0:14:06.76,Main,,0,0,0,,But, your other feeling...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.76,0:14:12.31,Main,,0,0,0,,...longed for the pleasant\Nsummer sun that shone on all things.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.81,0:14:15.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki was saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.86,0:14:19.32,Main,,0,0,0,,...that it was lonely being in the card alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.32,0:14:22.86,Main,,0,0,0,,She couldn't get out with walls parting her way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.86,0:14:28.12,Main,,0,0,0,,That must be the pain you held all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.54,0:14:34.54,Main,,0,0,0,,You hated being the only one enclosed\Nin the room, so to everyone you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.54,0:14:36.42,Main,,0,0,0,,So you're saying that Mayu...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.42,0:14:39.13,Main,,0,0,0,,...is all alone, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.25,0:14:41.55,Main,,0,0,0,,That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.55,0:14:45.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Mayu isn't alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.01,0:14:47.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Been a while since you've seen\Nme in this form, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.80,0:14:49.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Urith!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.10,0:14:51.85,Main,,0,0,0,,You wanted to become an\NLRIG to a strong Selector.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.85,0:14:54.35,Main,,0,0,0,,That's what you wished for, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.35,0:14:56.44,Main,,0,0,0,,But not me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.44,0:15:01.86,Main,,0,0,0,,I wanted to be an LRIG to a Selector\Nthat can bring greater despair to others.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.86,0:15:05.11,Main,,0,0,0,,And, that wish came true...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.11,0:15:10.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Mayu brought stories of endless\Nsuffering to countless numbers of girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.49,0:15:13.16,Main,,0,0,0,,She's my true Selector!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.41,0:15:17.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.88,0:15:21.55,Main,,0,0,0,,I've been wanting to slap that\Ndry, ignorant face of yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.55,0:15:23.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Come now... Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.47,0:15:27.89,Main,,0,0,0,,We didn't come here for battle!\NWe came here to talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.89,0:15:31.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Please, Mayu! Stop all\Nthese sad, heartless battles!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.68,0:15:34.14,Main,,0,0,0,,There's a more fun way to battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.14,0:15:35.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.43,0:15:38.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah... You're talking about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.52,0:15:43.15,Main,,0,0,0,,The battle conducted at the library\Ncourtyard with no wishes at stake...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.15,0:15:46.28,Main,,0,0,0,,A battle so boring that it made me yawn...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.28,0:15:49.12,Main,,0,0,0,,I know all about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.12,0:15:50.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.87,0:15:53.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's do it there, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.80,0:16:11.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Now, let's begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.60,0:16:14.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Show me how "fun" battles are, Ruko.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.81,0:16:16.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.23,0:16:19.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Battling Mayu won't change anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.81,0:16:22.27,Main,,0,0,0,,It's not like my wish would come true...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.27,0:16:24.57,Main,,0,0,0,,There could be meaning in doing this battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.57,0:16:26.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.07,0:16:28.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Mayu used to play WIXOSS all the time, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.65,0:16:31.91,Main,,0,0,0,,...she's never battled someone else before.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.91,0:16:36.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Being alone, she always battled\Nimaginary opponents she created.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.16,0:16:37.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.91,0:16:40.88,Main,,0,0,0,,I was able to change\Nthrough the battles with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.88,0:16:42.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.29,0:16:47.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Your battles held brilliance\Nthat can move people's hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.80,0:16:51.93,Main,,0,0,0,,What are you babbling about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.93,0:16:53.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Mayu is going to go first.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.97,0:16:55.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Urith. Grow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.78,0:17:11.28,Main,,0,0,0,,She's strong, but...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.28,0:17:14.70,Main,,0,0,0,,It looks like what you said was true, Yuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.70,0:17:19.79,Main,,0,0,0,,If we don't move to her predictions,\Nshe gets agitated and loses control.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.79,0:17:21.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Turn end!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.67,0:17:23.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.46,0:17:25.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Mayu! Hurry with the next order!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.84,0:17:28.38,Main,,0,0,0,,What...? Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.38,0:17:30.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Why isn't she attacking?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.80,0:17:33.14,Main,,0,0,0,,If Kuro attacked...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.14,0:17:37.89,Main,,0,0,0,,...I would gain enough Ener to\Nunleash Arts on Mayu's next turn...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.89,0:17:39.73,Main,,0,0,0,,--Why...?\N--Mayu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.39,0:17:44.02,Main,,0,0,0,,But... Mayu won't lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.02,0:17:46.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Because, it's about time...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.98,0:17:49.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Attack Ahriman with Brionac!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.16,0:17:57.29,Main,,0,0,0,,That didn't work one bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.29,0:18:01.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Kuro? Did you forget\Nthe rules of Selector battles?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.21,0:18:02.83,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.83,0:18:04.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Look at yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.46,0:18:13.63,Main,,0,0,0,,There was someone else to be\Nworried about besides Hanayo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.63,0:18:16.89,Main,,0,0,0,,With Urazoe Iona back in her body...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.89,0:18:18.39,Main,,0,0,0,,...Yuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.39,0:18:21.18,Main,,0,0,0,,...you're disqualified from being an Eternal Girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.18,0:18:23.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Y-Yuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.52,0:18:25.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.02,0:18:27.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Sooner or later, this was to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.48,0:18:28.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.78,0:18:32.65,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm a being that's never existed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.65,0:18:36.66,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm a character from a story that Mayu made.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.70,0:18:40.16,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm Yuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.16,0:18:41.95,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll disappear like the melting snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.95,0:18:42.87,Main,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.87,0:18:45.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Absolutely not, Yuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.71,0:18:47.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.34,0:18:49.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.75,0:18:52.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama can't come out of here...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.80,0:18:56.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Bring Tama to where Yuki is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.30,0:18:58.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.14,0:18:59.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.43,0:19:03.81,Main,,0,0,0,,What's holding you up?!\NHurry up and continue the battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.10,0:19:08.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko! What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.52,0:19:12.11,Main,,0,0,0,,You can't quit in the middle of battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.29,0:19:22.33,Main,,0,0,0,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.33,0:19:23.50,Main,,0,0,0,,The library?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.50,0:19:25.21,Main,,0,0,0,,This courtyard...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.21,0:19:27.75,Main,,0,0,0,,It's right up ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.26,0:19:39.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Another structure?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.64,0:19:44.14,Main,,0,0,0,,This library looks old, but it's still new.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.14,0:19:47.69,Main,,0,0,0,,I heard it was remodeled\Nfrom someone's mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.69,0:19:49.86,Main,,0,0,0,,I feel like I've seen that before...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.94,0:19:52.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.82,0:19:55.61,Main,,0,0,0,,It feels similar, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.61,0:19:57.57,Main,,0,0,0,,So then, Mayu's there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.57,0:19:59.32,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't know, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.32,0:20:00.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.37,0:20:07.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuki! Stay with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.04,0:20:10.46,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll take you to where Tama is right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.17,0:20:16.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.63,0:20:20.18,Main,,0,0,0,,That yard was exactly like\Nhow it was at the library, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.18,0:20:23.43,Main,,0,0,0,,...this place is so vague and abstract...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.43,0:20:25.22,Main,,0,0,0,,I think... I understand now...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.22,0:20:25.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.97,0:20:32.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Mayu kept Tama sealed away, not allowing\Nher to participate in Selector battles.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.11,0:20:35.65,Main,,0,0,0,,It bothered me as to why Tama awakened.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.65,0:20:39.53,Main,,0,0,0,,But... I think I understand now...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.53,0:20:41.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.37,0:20:42.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Mayu...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.74,0:20:46.45,Main,,0,0,0,,"No Trespassing"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.38,0:20:54.13,Main,,0,0,0,,No one's living here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.13,0:20:57.63,Main,,0,0,0,,What are you kids doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.63,0:21:02.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Um... We're friends with\Nthe girl who lives here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.14,0:21:05.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Hm? The girl here...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.47,0:21:07.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Mayu...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.06,0:21:10.39,Main,,0,0,0,,...probably died already...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.39,0:21:12.61,Main,,0,0,0,,That's right, Kuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.44,0:21:17.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Mayu is a dead girl now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.94,0:21:20.15,Main,,0,0,0,,M-Mayu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.15,0:21:25.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Kuro won't... leave Mayu\Nin true solitude, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.70,0:21:29.58,Main,,0,0,0,,You'll disappear with Mayu, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.58,0:21:32.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Grow, Urith. Level 5.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.47,0:21:46.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuki...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.85,0:21:48.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuki...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.81,0:21:50.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.93,0:21:52.98,Main,,0,0,0,,No... Say something...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.98,0:21:54.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.15,0:21:56.02,Main,,0,0,0,,N-No...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.02,0:21:58.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Nooo...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.48,0:22:01.99,Main,,0,0,0,,"That Locked Window"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.33,0:22:09.79,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Life...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.79,0:22:15.21,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A city of mazes with no exit{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.21,0:22:19.76,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and the sound of bells ringing{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.76,0:22:21.34,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I do...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.34,0:22:26.97,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Leave the "now" handed to me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.97,0:22:31.64,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}as I begin to walk in the morning{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.64,0:22:37.15,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In a world where light and dark intersect{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.15,0:22:43.32,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}catharsis begins to awake{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.32,0:22:48.41,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I swore in my shaking heart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.41,0:22:58.55,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}that I won't lose anyone anymore...!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.13,0:23:05.22,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if my tears flow tomorrow{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.22,0:23:11.93,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll run through the wind{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.93,0:23:16.98,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Release myself towards the future I selected{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.98,0:23:19.61,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}to regain it{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.61,0:23:26.70,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't give up on my wish{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.13,0:23:46.80,Main,,0,0,0,,"This Selection..."\NThis Selection...
